OL,6,FHe told the PA news agency that there
OL,7,Fwere parallels with the current row
OL,8,Fover the new law aimed at ensuring
OL,9,Fminimum levels of service during
OL,10,Fstrikes, which unions have warned is
OL,11,Funworkable.
OL,13,F"It doesn't matter how much the
OL,14,FGovernment tries to ban, bully and
OL,15,Fintimidate unions, we know that right
OL,16,Fis on our side.
