OL,3,CHuge rally to mark 40th anniversary of
OL,4,Cban on unions at GCHQ
OL,6,F"Their principled decision not to give
OL,7,Fup their trade union membership saw
OL,8,Fthem pay a massive price.
OL,10,F"Now, 40 years on, as we celebrate
OL,11,Ftheir courage and determination, a
OL,12,Fdifferent Conservative government is
OL,13,Fattacking trade union rights ` this
OL,14,Ftime they're introducing Minimum
OL,15,FService Levels in a naked attack on
OL,16,Four right to strike.
OL,18,F"Our message today is the same as it
OL,19,Fwas in 1984 ` we shall fight this
OL,20,Finjustice for however long it takes."
