OL,4,Cban on unions at GCHQ
OL,6,FChristina McAnea, general secretary of
OL,7,FUnison, told the PA news agency that
OL,8,Fthe Minimum Service Level law had
OL,9,Fechoes of the ban on union membership
OL,10,Fat GCHQ.
OL,12,F"Linking union membership with being
OL,13,Floyal to your country was an insult at
OL,14,FGCHQ, and it is similarly insulting to
OL,15,Fassume that public sector workers such
OL,16,Fas those in the NHS would not put the
OL,17,Fpublic first if they go on strike.
OL,19,F"The Tories have a blind spot when it
OL,20,Fcomes to working people."
